data.description: End of the road privacy in Virginia City Ranches. Nearly new de-titled manufactured home on a permanent, frost free foundation. This 6+/- acres has room for horses, shop, barn, etc. You will not get tired of the views from this location! Nice sized primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom & double vanity on one side of the house & the other two bedrooms on the other side of the house. Nook for your computer, crafts or homework. Rustic finishes, laundry room & pantry. Large deck to soak in the views & BBQ. Trail Creek is adjacent to, but not on the property of this low maintenance home.
